lead_paragraph: The Rio de Janeiro Olympic venue facing the most serious construction delay has hit another snag, with City Hall saying it is changing contractors for the track cycling velodrome.

headline.print_headline: Velodrome: Most Delayed Rio Olympic Venue Hits Another Snag
